org.modelio.api.modelio.model

Class ModelingSessionRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.api.modelio.model.ModelingSessionRegistry

  • public class ModelingSessionRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
    ModelingSessionRegistry maintains an application scoped unique map between CoreSession instances and SharedModelingSession instances. Registration and de-registration of sessions is carried out in org.modelio.api.impl.services.ModelioServices methods
    Since:
    5.1
